  <!-- ================================================================
       ORION  —  Top-level xacro (Gazebo Harmonic + ROS2 Jazzy)

       Plugin summary (all declared in sub-files):
         base.xacro    → gz_ros2_control (arm joint control)
         wheels.xacro  → gz-sim-mecanum-drive-system (/cmd_vel → /odom)
         sensors.xacro → gpu_lidar sensor on lidar_link (/scan)
         HERE          → gz-sim-sensors-system (needed to activate sensors)
                       → gz-sim-imu-system     (future IMU support)

       TODO: Bridge topics: (add to gazebo.launch.py)
         /scan         → sensor_msgs/msg/LaserScan
         /odom         → nav_msgs/msg/Odometry
         /cmd_vel      → geometry_msgs/msg/Twist
         /tf           → tf2_msgs/msg/TFMessage
         /clock        → rosgraph_msgs/msg/Clock
       ================================================================ -->
